726394f-a.text:
(1)
Cooper Ave., south side, between 81st Street (left) and 80th Street (right), showing the Henry Wolfert farmhouse from 1873-1896.
It was remodeled in 1923.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, showing a rear view looking east. On the north side of Cooper Ave. (electric wires thereon) is seen the property of the St.
John's Cemetery Corporation.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
